= Tumor types and Pathways  =


= How to use Tumor types and Pathways through the Biological Web Services Proxy =

In order to use the service the following [http://code.google.com/p/bwsproxy/wiki/parameters Proxy parameters] are requiered.

== Examples ==

http://bwsp.bioinfo.cnio.es/bwsp.php?bwsp_service=tumor-pathways&bwsp_response_format=json&bwsp_url=http://ws.bioinfo.cnio.es/rest/diseases/interactions/tab2graphml.php?threshold=0.1

http://bwsp.bioinfo.cnio.es/bwsp.php?bwsp_service=tumor-pathways&bwsp_response_format=json&bwsp_url=http://ws.bioinfo.cnio.es/rest/diseases/interactions/tab2graphml.php?threshold=0.01

http://bwsp.bioinfo.cnio.es/bwsp.php?bwsp_service=tumor-pathways&bwsp_response_format=json&bwsp_url=http://ws.bioinfo.cnio.es/rest/diseases/interactions/tab2graphml.php?threshold=0.001
